      { "@type": "Question", "name": "How much does central heating installation cost in Liverpool?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "A full central heating installation in Liverpool starts from £3,500 for a smaller property and can reach £6,000 to £7,000 for a larger home. This includes the boiler, all radiators, pipework, controls and Gas Safe certificate. Upgrading an existing system starts from £1,500. Adding a single radiator costs from £200 supply and fit. Liverpool rates are typically 10 to 15% lower than southern England. We provide a free written fixed-price quote after a site survey." } },
