    <div class="container">
      <h2>What Is Included in Your Liverpool Central Heating Installation</h2>
      <p class="pf-sub">No hidden extras. Here is everything included in the price we quote at your free survey.</p>

      <div class="pf-who-grid" style="margin-top:2rem;">
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>New A-rated boiler</strong><p>Worcester Bosch, Vaillant, Ideal or Baxi. Correctly sized for your property based on the number of radiators and hot water demand. All boilers are A-rated condensing models compliant with <a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/boiler-plus" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Boiler Plus regulations</a>.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Full radiator set designed for your property</strong><p>We design the radiator layout specifically for your home, calculating the correct output for each room based on size, insulation and heat loss. Every room gets the right amount of heat.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>All pipework routed and fitted</strong><p>All pipe routes are planned to minimise disruption to existing decoration where possible. We work neatly and clean up fully at the end of every working day.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Smart thermostat and heating controls</strong><p>A new smart thermostat and programmer installed and set up. Smart controls such as Nest or Hive available on request. Required under <a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/boiler-plus" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Boiler Plus regulations</a> for all new installations.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Magnetic system filter</strong><p>A magnetic filter is fitted to capture debris and sludge before it reaches the boiler heat exchanger. Required by most manufacturers to maintain the warranty and essential for long-term system health.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Inhibitor dosed to BS 7593 standard</strong><p>The system is filled with corrosion inhibitor dosed to the correct concentration. This protects all metal components from internal corrosion and is a warranty condition for all major boiler manufacturers.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Full system commissioning and balancing</strong><p>Every radiator is balanced individually to deliver the correct heat output. System pressure is set and a full heating and hot water cycle is run before we leave. Your new system works correctly from day one.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Gas Safe certificate and Benchmark certificate</strong><p>Both issued on the day of completion. The Gas Safe certificate is a legal requirement for any gas installation. The Benchmark certificate is required by all major manufacturers to register and validate the boiler warranty.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>12-month workmanship guarantee</strong><p>All our installations carry a 12-month workmanship guarantee in addition to the manufacturer warranty on the boiler itself. If anything fails as a result of our installation work, we return and resolve it at no cost.</p></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LIVERPOOL OLDER PROPERTIES -->
